 ikke s\u00e6rlige hensyn taler mot det. Det kan dreie seg om rikets sikkerhet eller personvern, sier Jagland til Dagbladet.", "Det er ikke bekreftet n\u00e5r Johaug-saken kommer opp i CAS. Kretsen rundt langrennsstjernen jobber imidlertid for at det skal skje i juni.", "(\u00a9NTB)"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "100sport"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "100sport|vintersport"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "100sport|vintersport|langrenn"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "e19a954ec4c50eb25ccbdac33cb083a8f9c24a7c89c1eeae457178ff92cc32e8"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-11T07:11:06.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Linda Hofstad Helleland (H) skal jobbe for at langrennsstjernens dopingh\u00f8ring i Idrettens voldgiftsrett (CAS) blir holdt for \u00e5pne d\u00f8rer."}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Vil ta opp Johaug-saken p\u00e5 WADAs styrem\u00f8te -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "990f91b786cdb0b877579a3b4b6d722aafd89fb6"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Linda Hofstad Helleland", "Johaug-saken", "FIS", "Therese Johaug"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Linda Hofstad Helleland,Johaug-saken,FIS,Therese Johaug"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["langrenn", "100sport", "vintersport"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "sports"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["\u00e5pne d\u00f8rer", "\u00e5pne"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["idrettens", "europas", "s. kretsen", "verdens antidopingbyr\u00e5", "s. det", "s. s\u00e5", "dagbladet"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["thorbj\u00f8rn jagland", "linda hofstad helleland", "therese johaug"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["100sport/vintersport", "100sport/vintersport/langrenn", "100sport"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "https://vertical.snd.no/images/d95cd431-2a8f-4e47-ba90-a1e09fbf836a?fit=crop&h=551&q=80&w=980"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field